attributes.title: Terrible app

attributes.review: I came to this app because I wanted to support America’s President. I left because the app and everything to do with it was dog****. It is extremely hard to navigate and the app crashes every other minute. The design and the layout are just horrid. It is a bad layout because nothing fits with my hands and there is no settings on the app where I can change the layout. There also is no diversity of information. Everyday it’s the same stuff over and over asking me to donate my life’s savings. I can’t believe that it crashes and I have the most up to date iPhone. I give it a 0/10 because of the difficulties in operating and navigating through it as well as it taking too much space in my phone. All day long I will be getting annoying notifications from the app and it is the most annoying thing I have ever downloaded. “Make America Great Again”, when was it ever great? During the young years of our nation when women had no rights and when we were exploiting the Natives? During the industrial revolution when slavery and war was ravaging our country? During WWII when millions of Americans were dying and there wasn’t equality among races and genders 150 years after our nation was founded on the basis of life liberty and the pursuit of happiness. Anyway, the app is just uncomfortable and annoying. Thank you for your time. @unusualbeing
